{
  "video_id": "5QTjSH1KGlY",
  "title": "A rite of passage for late life | Bob Stein",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12766.0,
      "end_time": 15924.0,
      "text": "I will never forget the first time I visited a client in jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17740.0,
      "end_time": 19281.0,
      "text": "The heavy, metal door slammed behind me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19305.0,
      "end_time": 21550.0,
      "text": "and I heard the key turn in the lock."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22198.0,
      "end_time": 25453.0,
      "text": "The cement floor underneath me had a sticky film on it"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25477.0,
      "end_time": 27190.0,
      "text": "that made a ripping sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27430.0,
      "end_time": 29657.0,
      "text": "like tape being pulled off a box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29681.0,
      "end_time": 31340.0,
      "text": "every time I moved my foot."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31955.0,
      "end_time": 36730.0,
      "text": "The only connection to the outside world was a small window placed too high to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37441.0,
      "end_time": 40496.0,
      "text": "There was a small, square table bolted to the floor"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40520.0,
      "end_time": 41972.0,
      "text": "and two metal chairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41996.0,
      "end_time": 43524.0,
      "text": "one on either side."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44354.0,
      "end_time": 47822.0,
      "text": "That was the first time I understood viscerally --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47846.0,
      "end_time": 50242.0,
      "text": "just for a fleeting moment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50267.0,
      "end_time": 52235.0,
      "text": "what incarceration might feel like."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52886.0,
      "end_time": 56887.0,
      "text": "And I promised myself all those years ago as a young, public defender"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56911.0,
      "end_time": 59529.0,
      "text": "that I would never, ever forget that feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60277.0,
      "end_time": 61659.0,
      "text": "And I never have."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62240.0,
      "end_time": 65975.0,
      "text": "It inspired me to fight for each and every one of my clients' freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65999.0,
      "end_time": 68131.0,
      "text": "as if it was my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69142.0,
      "end_time": 70467.0,
      "text": "Freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70832.0,
      "end_time": 74175.0,
      "text": "A concept so fundamental to the American psyche"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74199.0,
      "end_time": 76823.0,
      "text": "that it is enshrined in our constitution."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77839.0,
      "end_time": 82339.0,
      "text": "And yet, America is addicted to imprisonment."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82958.0,
      "end_time": 85510.0,
      "text": "From slavery through mass incarceration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85534.0,
      "end_time": 86867.0,
      "text": "it always has been."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87704.0,
      "end_time": 90631.0,
      "text": "Look, we all know the shocking numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90656.0,
      "end_time": 93308.0,
      "text": "The United States incarcerates more people per capita"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93332.0,
      "end_time": 96830.0,
      "text": "than almost any nation on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96938.0,
      "end_time": 101148.0,
      "text": "But what you may not know is that on any given night in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101172.0,
      "end_time": 105363.0,
      "text": "almost half a million people go to sleep in those concrete jail cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105387.0,
      "end_time": 108837.0,
      "text": "who have not been convicted of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109764.0,
      "end_time": 113538.0,
      "text": "These mothers and fathers and sons and daughters"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113562.0,
      "end_time": 117256.0,
      "text": "are there for one reason and one reason only:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117281.0,
      "end_time": 120428.0,
      "text": "they cannot afford to pay the price of their freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121312.0,
      "end_time": 124247.0,
      "text": "And that price is called bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125208.0,
      "end_time": 129300.0,
      "text": "Now, bail was actually created as a form of conditional release."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129539.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130375.99999999999,
      "text": "The theory was simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130400.0,
      "end_time": 133115.0,
      "text": "set bail at an amount that somebody could afford to pay --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133139.0,
      "end_time": 134296.0,
      "text": "they would pay it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134320.0,
      "end_time": 136844.0,
      "text": "it would give them an incentive to come back to court;"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136868.0,
      "end_time": 138835.0,
      "text": "it would give them some skin in the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138860.0,
      "end_time": 142836.0,
      "text": "Bail was never intended to be used as punishment."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142860.0,
      "end_time": 146834.0,
      "text": "Bail was never intended to hold people in jail cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146858.0,
      "end_time": 152830.0,
      "text": "And bail was never, ever intended to create a two-tier system of justice:"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152854.0,
      "end_time": 156810.0,
      "text": "one for the rich and one for everybody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156433.0,
      "end_time": 158995.0,
      "text": "But that is precisely what it has done."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159507.0,
      "end_time": 162899.0,
      "text": "75 percent of people in American local jails"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 162923.0,
      "end_time": 165226.0,
      "text": "are there because they cannot pay bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166215.0,
      "end_time": 167775.0,
      "text": "People like Ramel."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168514.0,
      "end_time": 170114.0,
      "text": "On a chilly October afternoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170138.0,
      "end_time": 172980.0,
      "text": "Ramel was riding his bicycle in his South Bronx neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173400.0,
      "end_time": 175382.0,
      "text": "on his way to a market to pick up a quart of milk."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 175760.0,
      "end_time": 177429.0,
      "text": "He was stopped by the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177454.0,
      "end_time": 180220.0,
      "text": "And when he demanded to know why he was being stopped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180460.0,
      "end_time": 182372.0,
      "text": "an argument ensued, and the next thing he knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182396.0,
      "end_time": 184170.0,
      "text": "he was on the ground in handcuffs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184410.0,
      "end_time": 187390.0,
      "text": "being charged with \"riding your bicycle on the sidewalk"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187630.0,
      "end_time": 188334.0,
      "text": "and resisting arrest.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188944.0,
      "end_time": 189994.0,
      "text": "He was taken to court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190180.0,
      "end_time": 192912.0,
      "text": "where a judge set 500 dollars bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192936.0,
      "end_time": 196800.0,
      "text": "But Ramel -- he didn't have 500 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 196320.0,
      "end_time": 199884.0,
      "text": "So this 32-year-old father was sent to \"The Boat\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199908.0,
      "end_time": 203612.0,
      "text": "a floating jail barge that sits on the East River"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 203636.0,
      "end_time": 206307.0,
      "text": "between a sewage plant and a fish market."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207241.0,
      "end_time": 209463.0,
      "text": "That's right, you heard me."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209487.0,
      "end_time": 212265.0,
      "text": "In New York City, in 2018,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 212289.0,
      "end_time": 216785.0,
      "text": "we have a floating prison barge that sits out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 216809.0,
      "end_time": 220216.0,
      "text": "and houses primarily black and brown men"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 220240.0,
      "end_time": 222387.0,
      "text": "who cannot pay their bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 223590.0,
      "end_time": 225235.0,
      "text": "Let's talk for a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 225259.0,
      "end_time": 228927.0,
      "text": "about what it means to be in jail even for a few days."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229368.0,
      "end_time": 232345.0,
      "text": "Well, it can mean losing your job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 232369.0,
      "end_time": 233702.0,
      "text": "losing your home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 233726.0,
      "end_time": 235793.0,
      "text": "jeopardizing your immigration status."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 236169.0,
      "end_time": 238943.0,
      "text": "It may even mean losing custody of your children."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 239598.0,
      "end_time": 242281.0,
      "text": "A third of sexual victimization by jail staff"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 242305.0,
      "end_time": 245760.0,
      "text": "happens in the first three days in jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 245100.0,
      "end_time": 249335.0,
      "text": "and almost half of all jail deaths, including suicides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249359.0,
      "end_time": 251166.0,
      "text": "happen in that first week."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251787.0,
      "end_time": 254907.0,
      "text": "What's more, if you're held in jail on bail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254931.0,
      "end_time": 257542.0,
      "text": "you're four times more likely to get a jail sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 257565.0,
      "end_time": 259176.0,
      "text": "than if you had been free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 259200.0,
      "end_time": 262183.0,
      "text": "and that jail sentence will be three times longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263360.0,
      "end_time": 267305.0,
      "text": "And if you are black or Latino and cash bail has been set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267329.0,
      "end_time": 271540.0,
      "text": "you are two times more likely to remain stuck in that jail cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271564.0,
      "end_time": 273105.0,
      "text": "than if you were white."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 274610.0,
      "end_time": 280347.0,
      "text": "Jail in America is a terrifying, dehumanizing and violent experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281574.0,
      "end_time": 286948.0,
      "text": "Now imagine for just one moment that it's you stuck in that jail cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286972.0,
      "end_time": 289656.0,
      "text": "and you don't have the 500 dollars to get out."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291720.0,
      "end_time": 295128.0,
      "text": "And someone comes along and offers you a way out."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 296145.0,
      "end_time": 297993.0,
      "text": "\"Just plead guilty,\" they say."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 298559.0,
      "end_time": 300655.0,
      "text": "\"You can go home back to your job."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301182.0,
      "end_time": 302612.0,
      "text": "Just plead guilty."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303300.0,
      "end_time": 305143.0,
      "text": "You can kiss your kids goodnight tonight.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305503.0,
      "end_time": 308679.0,
      "text": "So you do what anybody would do in that situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308703.0,
      "end_time": 312241.0,
      "text": "You plead guilty whether you did it or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313173.0,
      "end_time": 315650.0,
      "text": "But now you have a criminal record"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315674.0,
      "end_time": 318411.0,
      "text": "that's going to follow you for the rest of your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 319660.0,
      "end_time": 322772.0,
      "text": "Jailing people because they don't have enough money to pay bail"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 322796.0,
      "end_time": 326649.0,
      "text": "is one of the most unfair, immoral things we do as a society."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 327369.0,
      "end_time": 330409.0,
      "text": "But it is also expensive and counterproductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 331264.0,
      "end_time": 332759.0,
      "text": "American taxpayers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 332783.0,
      "end_time": 337425.0,
      "text": "they spend 14 billion dollars annually holding people in jail cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 337449.0,
      "end_time": 339338.0,
      "text": "who haven't been convicted of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 339362.0,
      "end_time": 341675.0,
      "text": "That's 40 million dollars a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 342820.0,
      "end_time": 346311.0,
      "text": "What's perhaps more confounding is it doesn't make us any safer."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346915.0,
      "end_time": 349417.0,
      "text": "Research is clear that holding somebody in jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 349441.0,
      "end_time": 353414.0,
      "text": "makes you significantly more likely to commit a crime when you get out"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 353438.0,
      "end_time": 357960.0,
      "text": "than if you had been free all along."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358440.0,
      "end_time": 361771.0,
      "text": "Freedom makes all the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 363574.0,
      "end_time": 364805.0,
      "text": "Low-income communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364829.0,
      "end_time": 368171.0,
      "text": "and communities of color have known that for generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 368750.0,
      "end_time": 373686.0,
      "text": "Together, they have pooled their resources to buy their loved ones freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 373710.0,
      "end_time": 377229.0,
      "text": "for as long as bondage and jail cells existed."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377891.0,
      "end_time": 381300.0,
      "text": "But the reach of the criminal legal system has grown too enormous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381270.0,
      "end_time": 383120.0,
      "text": "and the numbers have just too large."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 383809.0,
      "end_time": 388444.0,
      "text": "99 percent of jail growth in America has been the result --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 388468.0,
      "end_time": 390334.0,
      "text": "over the last 20 years --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390358.0,
      "end_time": 392373.0,
      "text": "of pre-trial incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394467.0,
      "end_time": 397143.0,
      "text": "I have been a public defender for over half my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397167.0,
      "end_time": 400832.0,
      "text": "and I have stood by and watched thousands of clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400857.0,
      "end_time": 402997.0,
      "text": "as they were dragged into those jail cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 403210.0,
      "end_time": 405373.0,
      "text": "because they didn't have enough money to pay bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405397.0,
      "end_time": 409952.0,
      "text": "I have watched as questions of justice were subsumed by questions of money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 409976.0,
      "end_time": 414145.0,
      "text": "calling into question the legitimacy of the entire American legal system."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 415213.0,
      "end_time": 418444.0,
      "text": "I am here to say something simple --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 418468.0,
      "end_time": 420146.0,
      "text": "something obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 420170.0,
      "end_time": 421759.0,
      "text": "but something urgent."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 422926.0,
      "end_time": 426181.0,
      "text": "Freedom makes all the difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 426205.0,
      "end_time": 429895.0,
      "text": "and freedom should be free."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 429919.0,
      "end_time": 436919.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 437919.0,
      "end_time": 440157.0,
      "text": "But how are we going to make that happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 440181.0,
      "end_time": 443181.0,
      "text": "Well, that's the question I was wrestling with over a decade ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 443206.0,
      "end_time": 446640.0,
      "text": "when I was sitting at a kitchen table with my husband, David,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 446880.0,
      "end_time": 447517.0,
      "text": "who is also a public defender."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 447541.0,
      "end_time": 451206.0,
      "text": "We were eating our Chinese takeout and venting about the injustice of it all"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 451230.0,
      "end_time": 453642.0,
      "text": "when David looked up and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453666.0,
      "end_time": 455550.0,
      "text": "\"Why don't we just start a bail fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 455574.0,
      "end_time": 457864.0,
      "text": "and just start bailing our clients out of jail?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 458836.0,
      "end_time": 461296.0,
      "text": "And in that unexpected moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 461320.0,
      "end_time": 464185.0,
      "text": "the idea for the Bronx Freedom Fund was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 467730.0,
      "text": "Look, we didn't know what to expect."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 467970.0,
      "end_time": 469712.0,
      "text": "There were plenty of people that told us we were crazy"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 469737.0,
      "end_time": 471737.0,
      "text": "and we were going to lose all of the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 471761.0,
      "end_time": 474904.0,
      "text": "People wouldn't come back because they didn't have any stake in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474928.0,
      "end_time": 476983.0,
      "text": "But what if clients did come back?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 477952.0,
      "end_time": 481723.0,
      "text": "We knew that bail money comes back at the end of a criminal case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 481747.0,
      "end_time": 483995.0,
      "text": "so it could come back into the fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 484190.0,
      "end_time": 488503.0,
      "text": "and we could use it over and over again for more and more bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 488527.0,
      "end_time": 489837.0,
      "text": "That was our big bet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 489861.0,
      "end_time": 491765.0,
      "text": "and that bet paid off."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 492393.0,
      "end_time": 493583.0,
      "text": "Over the past 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 493608.0,
      "end_time": 497280.0,
      "text": "we have been paying bails for low-income residents of New York City,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 497304.0,
      "end_time": 501205.0,
      "text": "and what we have learned has exploded our ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 501229.0,
      "end_time": 503430.0,
      "text": "of why people come back to court"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 503670.0,
      "end_time": 505755.0,
      "text": "and how the criminal legal system itself is operated."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 506533.0,
      "end_time": 510413.0,
      "text": "Turns out money isn't what makes people come back to court."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 510437.0,
      "end_time": 513374.0,
      "text": "We know this because when the Bronx Freedom Fund pays bail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 513398.0,
      "end_time": 517567.0,
      "text": "96 percent of clients return for every court appearance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 517591.0,
      "end_time": 521179.0,
      "text": "laying waste to the myth that it's money that mattered."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 521876.0,
      "end_time": 526910.0,
      "text": "It's powerful evidence that we don't need cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 526115.0,
      "end_time": 527375.0,
      "text": "or ankle bracelets"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 527399.0,
      "end_time": 530834.0,
      "text": "or unnecessary systems of surveillance and supervision."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 530858.0,
      "end_time": 533603.0,
      "text": "We simply need court reminders --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 533627.0,
      "end_time": 536615.0,
      "text": "simple court reminders about when to come back to court."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 537553.0,
      "end_time": 541648.0,
      "text": "Next, we learned that if you're held in jail on a misdemeanor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 541672.0,
      "end_time": 543983.0,
      "text": "90 percent of people will plead guilty."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 544603.0,
      "end_time": 546502.0,
      "text": "But when the fund pays bail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546526.0,
      "end_time": 549325.0,
      "text": "over half the cases are dismissed."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 550603.0,
      "end_time": 554459.0,
      "text": "And in the entire history of the Bronx Freedom Fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 554483.0,
      "end_time": 559180.0,
      "text": "fewer than two percent of our clients have ever received a jail sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 559204.0,
      "end_time": 560519.0,
      "text": "of any kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 560543.0,
      "end_time": 567519.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 568215.0,
      "end_time": 571104.0,
      "text": "Ramel, a week later --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571128.0,
      "end_time": 574457.0,
      "text": "he was still on the boat, locked in that jail cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 574481.0,
      "end_time": 576966.0,
      "text": "He was on the cusp of losing everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 576990.0,
      "end_time": 578933.0,
      "text": "and he was about to plead guilty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 578957.0,
      "end_time": 582155.0,
      "text": "and the Bronx Freedom Fund intervened and paid his bail."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582179.0,
      "end_time": 584116.0,
      "text": "Now, reunited with his daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 584140.0,
      "end_time": 586948.0,
      "text": "he was able to fight his case from outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 586972.0,
      "end_time": 588275.0,
      "text": "Look, it took some time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 588299.0,
      "end_time": 590363.0,
      "text": "two years, to be exact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 590387.0,
      "end_time": 591617.0,
      "text": "but at the end of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 591641.0,
      "end_time": 593966.0,
      "text": "his case was dismissed in its entirety."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 594928.0,
      "end_time": 596790.0,
      "text": "For Ramel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596103.0,
      "end_time": 601339.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 601364.0,
      "end_time": 606700.0,
      "text": "For Ramel, the Bronx Freedom Fund was a lifeline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 606310.0,
      "end_time": 608832.0,
      "text": "but for countless other Americans locked in jail cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 608856.0,
      "end_time": 610924.0,
      "text": "there is no freedom fund coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 611528.0,
      "end_time": 613595.0,
      "text": "It's time to do something about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 614173.0,
      "end_time": 616504.0,
      "text": "It's time to do something big."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 616528.0,
      "end_time": 618567.0,
      "text": "It's time to do something bold."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 619160.0,
      "end_time": 622394.0,
      "text": "It's time to do something, maybe, audacious?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 622418.0,
      "end_time": 623645.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 623669.0,
      "end_time": 626939.0,
      "text": "We want to take our proven, revolving bail-fund model"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 626963.0,
      "end_time": 628329.0,
      "text": "that we built in the Bronx"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 628353.0,
      "end_time": 630176.0,
      "text": "and spread it across America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 630201.0,
      "end_time": 632398.0,
      "text": "attacking the front end of the legal system"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 632422.0,
      "end_time": 634288.0,
      "text": "before incarceration begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 634312.0,
      "end_time": 636290.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 636314.0,
      "end_time": 639626.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 639650.0,
      "end_time": 645708.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 645732.0,
      "end_time": 646914.0,
      "text": "Here's the plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 646938.0,
      "end_time": 647990.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 648140.0,
      "end_time": 650253.0,
      "text": "We're going to bail out as many people as we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 650277.0,
      "end_time": 651511.0,
      "text": "as quickly as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 651535.0,
      "end_time": 652766.0,
      "text": "Over the next five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652791.0,
      "end_time": 655934.0,
      "text": "partnering with public defenders and local community organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 655958.0,
      "end_time": 658708.0,
      "text": "we're going to set up 40 sites in high-need jurisdictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 658732.0,
      "end_time": 661964.0,
      "text": "The goal is to bail out 160,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 662453.0,
      "end_time": 664640.0,
      "text": "Our strategy leverages the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 664890.0,
      "end_time": 666597.0,
      "text": "that bail money comes back at the end of a case."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 666621.0,
      "end_time": 667841.0,
      "text": "Data from the Bronx"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 667865.0,
      "end_time": 672676.0,
      "text": "shows that a dollar can be used two or three times a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 672700.0,
      "end_time": 675130.0,
      "text": "creating a massive force multiplier."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 675516.0,
      "end_time": 680665.0,
      "text": "So a dollar donated today can be used to pay bail for up to 15 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 680690.0,
      "end_time": 682699.0,
      "text": "over the next five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 683483.0,
      "end_time": 688551.0,
      "text": "Our strategy also relies on the experience and the wisdom and the leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 688576.0,
      "end_time": 692450.0,
      "text": "of those who have experienced this injustice firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 692474.0,
      "end_time": 694323.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 694347.0,
      "end_time": 698377.0,
      "text": "Each bail project site will be staffed by a team of bail disrupters."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 698903.0,
      "end_time": 702904.0,
      "text": "These are passionate, dedicated advocates from local communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 702928.0,
      "end_time": 705537.0,
      "text": "many of whom were formerly incarcerated themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 705561.0,
      "end_time": 707910.0,
      "text": "who will pay bails and support clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 707934.0,
      "end_time": 710411.0,
      "text": "while their cases are going through the legal system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 710435.0,
      "end_time": 713627.0,
      "text": "providing them with whatever resources and support they may need."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 714233.0,
      "end_time": 716849.0,
      "text": "Our first two sites are up and running."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 716874.0,
      "end_time": 718627.0,
      "text": "One in Tulsa, Oklahoma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 718651.0,
      "end_time": 720436.0,
      "text": "and one in St. Louis, Missouri."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 721120.0,
      "end_time": 722270.0,
      "text": "And Ramel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 722634.0,
      "end_time": 726158.0,
      "text": "He's training right now to be a bail disrupter in Queens County, New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 726182.0,
      "end_time": 731623.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 731647.0,
      "end_time": 733973.0,
      "text": "Our next three sites are ready to launch"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 733997.0,
      "end_time": 736977.0,
      "text": "in Dallas, Detroit and Louisville, Kentucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 737878.0,
      "end_time": 740807.0,
      "text": "The Bail Project will attack the money bail system"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 740831.0,
      "end_time": 742664.0,
      "text": "on an unprecedented scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 743369.0,
      "end_time": 747854.0,
      "text": "We will also listen, collect and elevate"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 747878.0,
      "end_time": 750243.0,
      "text": "and honor the stories of our clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 750267.0,
      "end_time": 752722.0,
      "text": "so that we can change hearts and minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 752746.0,
      "end_time": 756390.0,
      "text": "and we will collect critical, national data"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 756414.0,
      "end_time": 760540.0,
      "text": "that we need so we can chart a better path forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 760780.0,
      "end_time": 764808.0,
      "text": "so that we do not recreate this system of oppression in just another form."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 765434.0,
      "end_time": 766594.0,
      "text": "The Bail Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 766619.0,
      "end_time": 770228.0,
      "text": "by bailing out 160,000 people over the next five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 770252.0,
      "end_time": 773689.0,
      "text": "will become one of the largest non-governmental decarcerations"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 773714.0,
      "end_time": 775367.0,
      "text": "of Americans in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 775900.0,
      "end_time": 777500.0,
      "text": "So look --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 777750.0,
      "end_time": 779535.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 779559.0,
      "end_time": 782139.0,
      "text": "the criminal legal system, as it exists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 782163.0,
      "end_time": 784660.0,
      "text": "it needs to be dismantled."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 784900.0,
      "end_time": 786671.0,
      "text": "But here's the thing I know from decades in the system:"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 786695.0,
      "end_time": 789410.0,
      "text": "real, systemic change takes time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 789434.0,
      "end_time": 791236.0,
      "text": "and it takes a variety of strategies."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 791260.0,
      "end_time": 793415.0,
      "text": "So it's going to take all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 793440.0,
      "end_time": 795693.0,
      "text": "It's going to take the civil rights litigators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 795717.0,
      "end_time": 800146.0,
      "text": "the community organizers, the academics, the media, the philanthropists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 800170.0,
      "end_time": 802240.0,
      "text": "the students, the singers, the poets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 802264.0,
      "end_time": 806634.0,
      "text": "and, of course, the voices and efforts of those who are impacted by this system."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 807924.0,
      "end_time": 810365.0,
      "text": "But here's what I also know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 810389.0,
      "end_time": 813766.0,
      "text": "together, I believe we can end mass incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 814965.0,
      "end_time": 817770.0,
      "text": "But one last thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 817101.0,
      "end_time": 820641.0,
      "text": "those people, sitting in America, in those jail cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 820665.0,
      "end_time": 822966.0,
      "text": "in every corner of the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 822990.0,
      "end_time": 826296.0,
      "text": "who are held in jail on bail bondage, right now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 826320.0,
      "end_time": 828484.0,
      "text": "they need a lifeline today."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 829322.0,
      "end_time": 831348.0,
      "text": "That's where The Bail Project comes in."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 832770.0,
      "end_time": 835402.0,
      "text": "We have a proven model, a plan of action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 835426.0,
      "end_time": 837546.0,
      "text": "and a growing network of bail disrupters"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 837570.0,
      "end_time": 841390.0,
      "text": "who are audacious enough to dream big and fight hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 841414.0,
      "end_time": 844388.0,
      "text": "one bail at a time, for as long it takes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 844412.0,
      "end_time": 849162.0,
      "text": "until true freedom and equal justice are a reality in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 849589.0,
      "end_time": 850739.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 850763.0,
      "end_time": 857763.0,
